name: Tsurīsupiritto
description: Tsurīsupiritto is one of the well-known yokai. It appears to punish people who want to cut down rare tree species. She uses her sacred sledgehammer to destroy the chainsaws of people who want to cut down trees and make a frightening noise. He is in close contact with other yokai who protect the creatures in nature, and can help them once in a while.
